{"tid":26300,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我到而家都未知我有咩病...","createTime":"2016-12-06T15:48:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-10T16:50:03.000Z","uid":50821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"93b2b7e03545b972cdee465632b57562b066d8c0","tid":26300,"uid":50821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T15:48:38.000Z","msg":"還記得初中有一日朝早集會，三十幾度再加操場人口密度非常高，流汗當然係正常現象，就係果一日，我啲汗一流過脊椎位置，我成個人震咗震，唔係高潮果種震，係類似俾人嚇親果款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，自此之後惡夢就開始，每當背脊感覺到汗水流落去或者聽到後面近隔離嘅人聲，我都會震一震，特別係男人聲，因為把聲好沉，我真係好想好想解決呢個問題，到底有冇人經歷過或者有冇意思提供<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n認真一問求指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f8b7900594571866d05d057ecdf1b122ca00ef0","tid":26300,"uid":50821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T15:54:45.000Z","msg":"F5就爛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7853cdea434af255deb52f7a70606630f049f0f0","tid":26300,"uid":50892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T15:58:39.000Z","msg":"你會唔會有精神病呀？可能你根本無返學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08ca7cf238982583ad0e8f6592c1c9aa29f50307","tid":26300,"uid":50821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T16:09:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你會唔會有精神病呀？可能你根本無返學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真事 而家依然係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05f64c1ff5065c386813e1d0a24613b7a091a061","tid":26300,"uid":41266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T16:09:31.000Z","msg":"算係精神病 ，當你汗流只係你細個會唔會係比男性從後迫你做啲唔想做嘅嘢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81d856d9521bd12b3a7be2b011d32318355278c2","tid":26300,"uid":4